"*Miru* je nastalo iz riječi 'miriti' (Peace has come from the word 'miriti')

"On je doneo *mir* u zemlju" (He brought peace to the land)

"Oni su se sporazumjeli u ime *miru*" (They agreed in the name of peace)

"Dobrodošlica je bila upućena u ime *mira*" (The welcome was sent in the name of peace)

"Vladar je završio ratove za *mir*" (The ruler ended the wars for peace)

"Svi smo se zalagali za *mir*" (We all advocated for peace)